			"width": 400,
			"height": 160,
			"text": "# The Third Dimension\n\nThis canvas contains another canvas.\nYou're looking at **depth** — a spatial world\nthat holds another spatial world inside it.\n\nThis is the **3D prompt**.",
			"color": "6"
		},
