			"x": 480,
			"y": -40,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 200,
			"text": "# Why Nesting Matters\n\n**Overview** canvas → **Detail** canvas → **Sub-detail** canvas.\n\nAn agent navigating this sees structure at every level. It can zoom in for specifics or zoom out for the big picture.\n\nThe [[Concepts/The Mind Garden|mind garden]] grows in all directions.",
